{
  "stem": "7938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was the first action on a large scale.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was the action that nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Since it was the first one, there were no details known about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said that they are going to resettle the first people who don't work, or cannot have work in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They will be moved to the east for resettlement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and one day, it was surrendered-- it was surrounded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The whole ghetto was surrounded by soldiers, so that nobody can go out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody had to come out of the house, and to go on a place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In two places, they had it, and they checked everybody's identification.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they decided whether he can stay or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I stayed because I got from-- from the workplace, not from the workplace, but from the people who handled this-- this workplace.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I got this that they can have for me a job, so I stayed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My sister worked, so she went out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But my parents didn't work, so they knew that they were not good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When they assembled us all on the place, whoever didn't get the permission to stay had to go in-- in another-- in another line.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were loaded later on buses, and-- and from the buses on-- on the train and-- and further.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did not know where the people went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this was the biggest knockout that I got during the whole war-- the first one, and the biggest one-- when I lost my parents at that time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I-- I-- I felt inside that-- that although I didn't know where they're going, but they say to the east.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I understood that it will be a hard time that we will ever meet again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this became later known also.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
